snippet.description:
Presenting the Film Version of the Song "Aawaara Angaara" from the grand world of Shankar and Mukti - Tere Ishk Mein. Starring Dhanush and Kriti Sanon.

Gulshan Kumar, T-Series and Colour Yellow present
An A. R. Rahman Musical
‚ÄúTERE ISHK MEIN‚Äù

A Film By Aanand L Rai

Produced by Aanand L Rai, Himanshu Sharma
Produced by Bhushan Kumar, Krishan Kumar
Written by Himanshu Sharma, Neeraj Yadav

Running Successfully In Cinemas Worldwide in Hindi, Tamil and Telugu.

#Jaani #BPraak #NewMusic 

Lyrics - 

Ek Toh Parvardigaar Ke Baare Mein Na Boliye
Aur Phir Aitbaar Ke Baare Mein Na Boliye
Aapka Hum Qatal Bhi Kar Sakte Hain
Aap Hamare Yaar Ke Baare Mein Na Boliye

Humse Woh Mila Hi Nahin Hai Sadiyon Se
Taras Gaye The Hum Yaar Ke Saath Ko
Us Bewafa Ka Dil Kaat Ke Dekhna Hai
Woh Kiske Liye Roya Tha Kal Raat Ko

Mera Dil Gaya Dil Gaya Dil Gaya Dil Gaya
Dil Gaya Dil Gaya Bewafa
Mainu Mil Gaya Mil Gaya Mil Gaya Mil Gaya
Mil Gaya Mil Gaya Bewafa

Mujhe Toh Rulaya Hi Hai
Mujhe Toh Hasaya Hi Nahin
Mujhme Kami Kya Thi
Yaar Ne Bataya Hi Nahin

Teri Hi Gali Se Mera Guzra Janaza Tha
Maine Awaaz Di Thi Tu Baahar Aaya Hi Nahin

Tere Kolon Choor Hoke Enni Majboor Hoke
Haukeyan Lag Gayi Aan Main
Paagal Banayi Payi Aan
Jama Hi Hilaayi Payi Aan
Nasheyan Te Lag Gayi Aan Main
Ho Jaani Hai Mera Dushman

Main Aisi Nazar Utaarungi
Tu Beech Mein Aa Na Duniya
Jaani Ko Main Hi Maarungi

Woh Gala Bhi Mera Kaate Toh Koi Baat Nahin
Main Kaat Nahin Sakti Uski Baat Ko

Us Bewafa Ka Dil Kaat Ke Dekhna Hai
Woh Kiske Liye Roya Tha Kal Raat Ko

Kitne Deewane Rakh Rakhe Hain God Mein
Ik Aane Lag Jaata Hai Ik Jaane Lag Jaata Hai
Aapke Pairon Se Kya Mohabbat Hai Duniya Ko
Jo Aata Hai Dabaane Lag Jaata Hai

Hai Soyi Thi Kabar Mein Woh Jag Gayi Kya Bolun
Mujhe Uski Aisi Aadat Lag Gayi Hai Kya Bolun

Main Jugnu Ko Bolun Sooraj
Aur Bande Ko Khuda Bolun
Mujhe Uski Aisi Aadat Lag Gayi Hai Kya Bolun

Mere Pairon Mein Jo Chubh Gaye
Woh Kaante Kaun Nikaalega
Oh Hai Koi Yahan Bola
Jo Ik Laash Ko Paa Lega

Woh Phir Bhi Hai Jaan Meri
Meri Pehchaan Rahega Woh
Jaan Woh Tha Jaan Hai Woh
Aage Bhi Jaan Rahega Woh

Maine Yaar Mere Ko Chhoda Tha Sava Saat Baje
Woh Kisi Aur Ka Ho Gaya Paune Aath Ko

Us Bewafa Ka Dil Kaat Ke Dekhna Hai
Woh Kiske Liye Roya Tha Kal Raat Ko

Yeh Aajkal Sabko Kya Ho Gaya Hai
Bure Logon Ki Ho Rahi Hai Umr Lambi
Achhe Log Mar Jaa Rahe Hain

Us Bewafa Ka Dil Kaat Ke Dekhna Hai

Two intense days. Countless battles. Clutches, comebacks, chaos ‚Äî and it all comes down to THIS.

India vs South Africa 1st T20 Match, Aaj Ki Raat, 7 bajy se

When: Tuesday, December 9, 2025 at 7 PM local time

Where: Barabati Stadium, Cuttack

What to expect: With a new red-soil base, the Barabati surface bears resemblance to the Wankhede track - a typical T20 wicket, full of runs. Having lost both of their previous games against South Africa at this venue, India will be keen to break the trend. IND vs SA, 1st T20 Match, Aaj Ki Raat 7 bajy Star Sports per.

Team News

India

Players are all fit with slight uncertainty over Hardik Pandya, who experienced discomfort while bowling at the nets on Sunday evening. With Shubman Gill opening with Abhishek Sharma, there is unlikely to be a place in the XI for Sanju Samson. Shivam Dube will be the third pacer which means Arshdeep Singh may sit out.

Probable XI: Suryakumar Yadav (C), Shubman Gill (VC), Abhishek Sharma, Tilak Varma, Hardik Pandya, Shivam Dube, Axar Patel, Jitesh Sharma (WK), Jasprit Bumrah, Varun Chakaravarthy, Kuldeep Yadav.

South Africa

Aiden Markram is back as South Africa captain for the T20Is after being rested for the limited-overs series against Pakistan a few weeks back. He's set to open with Quinton de Kock while it remains to be seen if Tony de Zorzi, who picked up an injury in the second ODI, has made sufficient recovery. Dewald Brevis and Tristan Stubbs will form the middle order core along with David Miller, who is set to return after a hamstring injury forced him to miss the Pakistan series. Among the bowlers, Anrich Nortje is set to make his first international appearance since the 2024 T20 World Cup final against India. Nortje might prove useful early on against Shubman Gill, having dismissed the Indian opener 4 times in 7 innings in T20 cricket, while he has also accounted for India captain Suryakumar Yadav twice in six innings.

Probable XI: Quinton de Kock (wk), Aiden Markram (c), Tony de Zorzi, Dewald Brevis, Tristan Stubbs, David Miller, Marco Jansen, Corbin Bosch, Keshav Maharaj, Lungi Ngidi, Anrich Nortje

After winning the ODI Series Against South Africa by 2-1, Now Blue shirts have to play 5 T20 Match series against the guest.

India vs South Africa Highlights Today
India have to play almost 10 T20i Matches before the ICC Men's T20 Cricket World Cup 2026. This is an opportunity to maintain momentum & chose the best 11 players for upcoming event. After the 3 match ODI Series, India will play 5 T20 Match Matches against South Africa at home. Afterwards, New Zealand cricket team will visit India.

Here is the teams list that will participate in the next T20 World Cup 2026.

T20 World Cup 2026 teams and groups
Group A: India, Pakistan, Netherlands, Namibia, USA.
Group B: Sri Lanka, Australia, Zimbabwe, Ireland, Oman.
Group C: England, West Indies, Bangladesh, Nepal. Italy.
Group D: South Africa, New Zealand, Afghanistan, UAE, Canada. India vs Pakistan T20 Cricket World Cup Match Will be played on February 15 2026.

snippet.description:
Official music video for En Yesu by Stella Ramola and Daniel Davidson.

Listen to Stella Ramola‚Äôs album, Journey, here:
https://stellaramola.lnk.to/Journey

Allan Abraham
Joshua Paul David

Karunya Deemed University
Catherine Stree
Roy‚Äôs Wonderland 
& our well-wishers from social media

Lyrics:
Irulile velichamaai vandhavar ivare
(He is the One who came as light into the darkness)
Idhayathin deebamaai irupavar ivare
(He is the One who remains as the lamp of my heart)

Idhuvarai kandadhil sirandhavar ivare
(He is the greatest One I have ever seen till now)
Inimaiyin uruvamaai pirandhavar ivare
(He is the One born as the embodiment of sweetness)
Mudhalum mudivumaai irupavar ivare
(He is the One who is the Beginning and the End)
En vazhkaiyin arthum ivare
(He is the meaning of my life)

Avar saaronin roja
(He is the Rose of Sharon)
Pallathakin leeli
(The Lily of the Valleys)
Vidivelli natchathram
(The Morning Star)
En Yesu
(My Jesus)

1. Yelmaiyaaga pirandhavarae
(He who was born in humility)
Thazhmaiyaaga vazharndhavarae
(He who lived in meekness)
Thanaithaan veruthu adimaiyin roobam eduthu
(He emptied Himself and took the form of a servant)
Than uyirai koduthu nammai sondhamaakinaar
(He gave His life and made us His own)

2. Kaayangalai aatridave
(To heal wounds)
Idhayangalai thetridave
(To restore hearts)
Ivvulagil vaazhum tham maanthargalukkaaga
(For the people living in this world)
Rajaadhi rajaavaai meendhum varugiraar
(He is coming back as the King of kings)

snippet.title: Tu Is Tarah Se Mere Zindagi Main | Mohammed Rafi | Aap To Aise Na The | Raj Babbar | Classic Song
snippet.description:
Enjoy the song ''Tu Is Tarah Se Meri Zindagi Mein Shameel Hai" with Hindi & English Lyrics sung by Mohammed Rafi from the movie Aap To Aise Na The. The melody, composed by the talented Usha Khanna, is both melodious and evocative, enhancing the song's emotional depth. Rafi's voice brings a soulful quality to the track, making it one of his memorable performances.

Enjoy Mohammad Rafi's best songs only on @MohammedRafiOldMelodies 
Subscribe now!

Credit:
Song: Tu Is Tarah Se Mere Zindagi Main
Album: Aap To Aise Na The
Artist: Mohammed Rafi
Music Director: Usha Khanna, Kamal Joshi
Lyricist: Nida Fazli
Film Star: Ranjeeta, Raj Babbar, Deepak Parashar, Tamanna, Madan Puri, Om Shivpuri, Dulari, Kalpana Iyer
Director: Ambrish Singal

Lyrics:-
Tu is tarah se meri zindagi mein shamil hai

Tu is tarah se meri zindagi mein shamil hai

Jahan bhi jaaun yeh lagta hai teri mehfil hai

Tu is tarah se meri zindagi mein shamil hai


Yeh asmaan, yeh baadal, yeh raste, yeh hawa

Yeh asmaan, yeh baadal, yeh raste, yeh hawa

Har ek cheez hai apni jagah thikaane se

Kayi dinon se shikaayat nahin zamane se

Yeh zindagi hai safar, tu safar ki manzil hai

Jahan bhi jaaun yeh lagta hai teri mehfil hai

Tu is tarah se meri zindagi mein shamil hai


Tere baghair jahan mein koyi kami si thi

Tere baghair jahan mein koyi kami si thi

Bhatak rahi thi jawani andheri raahon mein

Sukhun dil ko mila aake teri baahon mein

Main ek khoyi hui mauj hoon, tu saahil hai

Jahan bhi jaaun yeh lagta hai teri mehfil hai

Tu is tarah se meri zindagi mein shamil hai


Tere jamaal se roshan hai qaaynat meri

Tere jamaal se roshan hai qaaynat meri

Meri talaash teri dilkashi rahe baaki

Khuda kare ke yeh dewangi rahe baaki

Teri wafaa hi meri har khushi ka haasil hai

Jahan bhi jaaun yeh lagta hai teri mehfil hai

Tu is tarah se meri zindagi mein shamil hai

snippet.description:
A love story of ego, spark, and two people who know they‚Äôll never find another like each other. Shivjot x Gurlez Akhtar bring fire in ‚ÄúTere Jehi‚Äù.
New punjabi song ‚ÄúTere Jehi‚Äù is a fiery Punjabi duet by Shivjot and Gurlez Akhtar, capturing the playful fights, ego, and chemistry between a proud gabhru and a bold fashion-freak Jatti. Both claim no one can match them, yet neither can replace the other. Powered by The Boss‚Äôs energetic bhangra music and dancing beats, the track blends attitude, romance, and signature Punjabi flair ‚Äî a perfect mix of swag, emotion, and dance-floor energy.
